{"type":"message","id":"ce5aebfd","parentId":"af7f862d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:09:26.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到问题了！`web.search.enabled` 是 `false`，而且没有配置 Tavily API Key。昨天可能配置了但没有保存，或者被覆盖了。\n\n让我帮用户添加 Tavily 配置。Tavily 的 API Key 需要用户提供。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。`web.search.enabled` 被设成了 `false`，而且没看到 Tavily 的配置。\n\n昨天配的没保存下来。你需要重新设置一下：\n\n```\nopenclaw configure --section web\n```\n\n或者在配置里直接加（需要你的 Tavily API Key）：\n\n```json\n\"web\": {\n  \"search\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"apiKey\": \"你的Tavily API Key\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n你有 Tavily 的 API Key 吗？有的话我直接帮你写进去。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding-2","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1793,"output":170,"cacheRead":40704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773893360360}}
